Name: KEEK
About the game: KEEK is a pixel 2D platformer that you could use a special force to change the dimension of objects. Overcome obstacles, disable traps, collect items and face the final challenge. Feature Fine and detailed pixel art Change dimension, play through impossible levels Hidden elements This game was originally created for GCORES BOOOM Challenge 2021. A full release version is under development.
